
The project kit, for people or project to make their own button. 

The aim is t model the project components

1. a button (made by the data subject)
2. a form letter that is filled in with 
3. the data subject details, ( populates the form)
4. legal references. 

1. Once org fills in form - then it sends the second part of the Data subject request. 
2. A request to do: X (during the hackathon we brainstorm X)
3. responses go direct to Data subjects - through the form created
3. Project kits, - make buttons.  (hosted for Privacy Day) 

People sign up, 
stage 1: register interest/sign petitiion (check box)
Stage 2: send email to setup button. 
Stage 3: press button and tweet - IFTTT

